     TTTTrrrraaaaiiiinnnniiiinnnngggg
             Training mode lets you interactively guess the moves
             of a game for one of the players. You guess the next
             move of the game by playing the move on  the  board.
             If  the  move  played  matches  the next move of the
             game,  the  move  is  accepted  and  the  opponent's
             response  is  autoplayed.   If  the  move  played is
             incorrect, an error message is displayed.   You  can
             select this mode only while loading a game (that is,
             after selecting  Load  Game  from  the  File  menu).
             While  xboard  is  in  Training mode, the navigation
             buttons are disabled.

